<h1>Hi5Sport – Account Deletion</h1>

<p>You can delete your account directly in the app:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Open Hi5Sport</li>
  <li>Go to "My Profile"</li>
  <li>Scroll down</li>
  <li>Tap "Delete my account"</li>
  <li>Confirm deletion</li>
</ol>

<p><strong>All your personal data will be permanently deleted.</strong></p>

<p>Data deleted includes:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Profile information</li>
  <li>Activities</li>
  <li>Messages</li>
  <li>Matches</li>
</ul>

<p>If you have any issues, contact: support@hi5sport.app</p>

